The paper deals with graph construction, which is a fundamental operation in data processing pipelines. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA). However, since the paper focuses on the mathematical criteria for determining the structure of adjacency arrays, it is most likely to belong to cs.DM. The other sub-categories are also possible because they deal with topics related to graph theory and data processing.
